{
  "version": "1",
  "questId": "fr_08",
  "lang": "hu",
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "000fc05",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Egy meleg sapka melegen tartja a fejed.",
      "sourceEnText": "A warm hat keeps your head warm.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_000fc05.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:35Z",
      "textHash": "4850bda2630284c31d7df821964b63ab5aee6549252ea550b6fc31a1282fe70d"
    },
    {
      "key": "001e940",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Válaszoljunk három hegyi kérdésre a zászlójáték előtt.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's answer three mountain questions before the flag game.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_001e940.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:41:42Z",
      "textHash": "9610317d59db978cf55bb58aee3b903e22c9e4cd982fd3a00d75f03feee1aad0"
    },
    {
      "key": "003e87c",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_bonus",
      "sourceText": "Találtál egy meleg sálat!",
      "sourceEnText": "You found a warm scarf!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003e87c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1593,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:18Z",
      "textHash": "09c8d9e17611beb276ced676338630e186d6017ca47209f60920f4e907a488cf"
    },
    {
      "key": "003ecb2",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "A Mont Blanc az Alpok legmagasabb hegye!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mont Blanc is the highest mountain in the Alps!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003ecb2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:20Z",
      "textHash": "b01abab88bff8643b5f79e13770d3ca3509bfaeb64a6833b3ce0136486f730ed"
    },
    {
      "key": "00a7e83",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Helyes! Használd őket, hogy stabil maradj.",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct! Use them to stay steady.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_00a7e83.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:50Z",
      "textHash": "2dc82b0bacdae50dbf6f999e8533706ed1199bf1f42a84d4e14e38a3e5d8a8bd"
    },
    {
      "key": "011dc7e",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Imádom a hegyeket!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love the mountains!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_011dc7e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1280,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:20Z",
      "textHash": "ad6192e5cd0bead99c9c8a52ffa458cb04c5edb705899416992f49db40c64e98"
    },
    {
      "key": "015bf8a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Most már készen állsz a mászásra!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are now ready to climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_015bf8a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2011,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:29Z",
      "textHash": "b276dae3509c03fae19c2db0690cc7f9b7214270e41db70b54b5031e4fd4454e"
    },
    {
      "key": "018880a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Ez a csúcs 4807 méter magas.",
      "sourceEnText": "This summit is 4807 meters high.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_018880a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:56Z",
      "textHash": "1135fa076982d6158894ed7e3fec68d2ebfe39252f4728229858e679f74c8ed3"
    },
    {
      "key": "01a4b20",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Ujjbékák",
      "sourceEnText": "Flippers",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01a4b20.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1045,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:51Z",
      "textHash": "1fda71e3b968c4a0328ad0bf0f63d53d81a7d381bf59dc1dd94e5fdf3261049c"
    },
    {
      "key": "01beb5e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Láttuk a kutyát felfutni a hegyre.",
      "sourceEnText": "We saw the dog run up the mountain.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01beb5e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:23Z",
      "textHash": "9d9a466f9042dfee78007b01b7d966eaa4bc9564499b7086f0a2d5ef2198300e"
    },
    {
      "key": "01e5f66",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Ez a gleccser úgy néz ki, mint egy befagyott folyó.",
      "sourceEnText": "That glacier looks like a frozen river.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01e5f66.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2952,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:26Z",
      "textHash": "d3438a20d3bbf4794b410d1acce911672e7313a11c9edceeda2fb3bb1c32533d"
    },
    {
      "key": "029a03e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "A nap nagyon fényesen süt a havon. Szemvédelemre van szükségünk.",
      "sourceEnText": "The sun on the snow is very bright. We need eye protection.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029a03e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4284,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:39Z",
      "textHash": "3d69071bd724a4daa5b90ddecbe87095b9825341228f2026c547cd51dd542c45"
    },
    {
      "key": "029f39c",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "Most már elhagyhatjuk az alaptábort és elkezdhetjük a kalandot!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now we can exit the base camp and start the adventure!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029f39c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3605,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:28Z",
      "textHash": "895f45d072eea3d21b465a72e2d82e5c5cf9377e69721e0589da62bb3a997598"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a2ea9",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "A hó és a jég visszaveri a ragyogó napfényt.",
      "sourceEnText": "Snow and ice reflect bright sunlight.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a2ea9.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2664,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:45Z",
      "textHash": "ebacaa45546aba295b4e57d48d8786762bb8c60f1c4ad10d0d94975595cbaa44"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a3874",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Nem, itt maradok",
      "sourceEnText": "No, I stay here",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a3874.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 940,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:15Z",
      "textHash": "d5795932a38c723db98be3d787a1b9727df611fafd620f69b1074e470822ab16"
    },
    {
      "key": "02c9805",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_3_done",
      "sourceText": "Nyisd ki a mellkast, hogy hágóvasakat kapj!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get crampons!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02c9805.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2351,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:52Z",
      "textHash": "2bd54e9244bbc7f77b0109085457860a576815c7fad321efe5bf736273ddd26c"
    },
    {
      "key": "030fa1c",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Sikerült! A Mont Blanc tetején vagyunk.",
      "sourceEnText": "You made it! We are at the top of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_030fa1c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2377,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:55Z",
      "textHash": "04e348f773917e3bd110af9dede6419c7619dda60b40f4a72fda791a40c4d7fb"
    },
    {
      "key": "035e68a",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "4. alaptábor",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 4",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_035e68a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1358,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:14Z",
      "textHash": "d590a2d15191cf278c5fb56b453853a9f4751662c4691c8e13ac3c181b5716f0"
    },
    {
      "key": "0371d31",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Az idegenvezetővel való mászás biztonságosabb.",
      "sourceEnText": "Climbing with a guide is safer.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0371d31.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 3213,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:28Z",
      "textHash": "e356a451d5ae305fac6e578232b446ac256144814b3676e66d5027b03e581e92"
    },
    {
      "key": "038d1bc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_rope",
      "sourceText": "A kötél segít a hegymászóknak biztonságban maradni jégen és sziklán.",
      "sourceEnText": "The rope helps climbers stay safe on ice and rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_038d1bc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4232,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:54Z",
      "textHash": "98d6d09776a35fdff5513dac4f6c7ce6b3de171245d3531309c0a14d777d2c90"
    },
    {
      "key": "03db010",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_swiss",
      "sourceText": "Svájc a Mont Blanc-tól északra található.",
      "sourceEnText": "Switzerland is north of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03db010.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:41:45Z",
      "textHash": "4e19abc867e3a5efffa2d696a478319320cb5cef45dc0306cb2517a5136107ab"
    },
    {
      "key": "03dd802",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Hiányzik a kabátod!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the coat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03dd802.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1515,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:31Z",
      "textHash": "3e4fe6c98f205bbab0dc5b779c3dc8f1c8a01c71e72b570b5fa61fafa69885f0"
    },
    {
      "key": "045409f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Indulás előtt szükséged lesz egy hátizsákra.",
      "sourceEnText": "Before going, you need a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_045409f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2612,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:25Z",
      "textHash": "9e039ba3e00f07a08bab0ed46e5c23b4c6877228bb70ecc4fcd98eacdc4bc74f"
    },
    {
      "key": "046eb33",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Gyere vissza, ha befejezted a feladatot.",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back when you finish the task.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_046eb33.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:21Z",
      "textHash": "766caa10c96ffd53e9aa132c16f29d277cf60e945e5d654d6f7fa6edc79d027a"
    },
    {
      "key": "04bbada",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Remélem, látok majd egy mormotát!",
      "sourceEnText": "I hope to see a marmot!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04bbada.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1933,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:21Z",
      "textHash": "6b375c3965224e99322ef78f7308349e4c0672743ce46cb6fa28fadf86c981b2"
    },
    {
      "key": "04c1c1f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Látom, nálad van a hátizsák. Most már mehetsz!",
      "sourceEnText": "I see you have the backpack. Now you can go!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04c1c1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2769,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:19Z",
      "textHash": "cc70b988a5c656574eab22399647b8c2b156d6328964e6cf328000ea75791534"
    },
    {
      "key": "050fe70",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_italy",
      "sourceText": "Olaszország a Mont Blanc-tól keletre található.",
      "sourceEnText": "Italy is east of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_050fe70.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3082,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:41:44Z",
      "textHash": "a39e0ddcf4b62660428d390b49a2e5687240f2a7094bb32796e4833b5299d090"
    },
    {
      "key": "0557ef5",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "A szél gyorsan változhat.",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind can change fast.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0557ef5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 1881,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:24Z",
      "textHash": "3e88574658f217f3411c10efcd02b4d9de071f2e0407e634308c3ef7f61e9ceb"
    },
    {
      "key": "056ec2b",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base1",
      "sourceText": "Nyílik! Van benne valami felszerelés.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains some equipment.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_056ec2b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:34Z",
      "textHash": "f60d2a5e10b4b68a48f49d99e2ca87e93b10fc52519deedc588d7c04be06cde3"
    },
    {
      "key": "058bb65",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "3. alaptábor",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 3",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_058bb65.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1358,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:14Z",
      "textHash": "e89a6e3d1c8968ccd0973702ef49dc97453db845a4ecda4d65d2feeab138c8c5"
    },
    {
      "key": "0590129",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Ne felejts el meleg ruhát hozni!",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't forget to bring warm clothes!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0590129.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2011,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:22Z",
      "textHash": "44f8891c6c610993dcc1a30b295a57bf46f40b02dc850935872c8be8673e3592"
    },
    {
      "key": "059d744",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Az is segít, ha hideg a szél.",
      "sourceEnText": "It also helps when the wind is cold.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_059d744.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1698,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:36Z",
      "textHash": "39de863573dd03ba59ca833df75f46718c389701fcc956055ae365508e141c4c"
    },
    {
      "key": "05cabb5",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Nézz körül érte!",
      "sourceEnText": "Look around for it!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05cabb5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1228,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:25Z",
      "textHash": "5cb17f7b2caa3682aa14491c7d138d715d7f148e08644c4f2eddf4ce9dda983d"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e3658",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "2. alaptábor",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 2",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e3658.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1045,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:34:13Z",
      "textHash": "3249d9ddeda53bc910ef3ab33bde2ef8296ddfe932300e85c802f228615d7892"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e80cb",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "Ez a hátizsák élelmiszert, vizet és térképet is képes szállítani.",
      "sourceEnText": "This backpack can carry food, water, and a map.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e80cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4624,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:28Z",
      "textHash": "f290330660b05b0c821d11b031fb747686e8898b5433c0dcb2cc97f70ae31744"
    },
    {
      "key": "0650acc",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Fedezd fel a Mont Blanc-t és keresd fel felszerelésünket!",
      "sourceEnText": "Please explore Mont Blanc and find our gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0650acc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3318,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:24Z",
      "textHash": "b72315f773a5654cccdc1977f85571a1464f5ad7784ea8ba1dd6cad2c23e4f24"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b15bb",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Megvan a jégfelszerelés. Egy utolsó lökés a csúcsra!",
      "sourceEnText": "You have the ice gear. One last push to the top!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b15bb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:46Z",
      "textHash": "6a0f725516041b14b0f3721815bc502a078acdf362fe2b6a142b419833e0bba3"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b3363",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Hiányzik a kesztyűd!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the gloves!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b3363.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1463,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:38Z",
      "textHash": "ab6e557d1b1fea19bb8b2fdaf5cbca7ede6066eda4b3a37ff8c3f3db4d5a40de"
    },
    {
      "key": "06d9f34",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "A gleccserek jégén való járáshoz speciális felszerelésre van szükségünk.",
      "sourceEnText": "To walk on glacier ice, we need special gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06d9f34.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4519,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:48Z",
      "textHash": "0b7a8dd839f79d5ad5798fc4e11410b8fc8d30c93f36ffcb005a8a70fcddd383"
    },
    {
      "key": "06f9a2a",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Melyik hegységben található a Mont Blanc?",
      "sourceEnText": "What mountain range is Mont Blanc in?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06f9a2a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:58Z",
      "textHash": "bae7f47bdb8c999103a897c576f0fbc3a3654548e27318179971a0e1430d0f3d"
    },
    {
      "key": "07102e7",
      "nodeTitle": "item_crampons",
      "sourceText": "Ezek segítenek biztonságosan közlekedni a jégen.",
      "sourceEnText": "These help you walk safely on ice.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07102e7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "shelley",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2952,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:33:53Z",
